data.title: Rahul Mahajan ex-wife Dimpy Ganguly welcomes second baby
data.meta_description: Dimpy Ganguly's ex-wife Dimpy Ganguly's house is buzzing once again. Simultaneously Dimpy has given birth to a son. Dimpy herself sh... | News Track
data.text:
Dimpy Ganguly's ex-wife Dimpy Ganguly's house is buzzing once again. Simultaneously Dimpy has given birth to a son. Dimpy herself shared this information on social media. Also, after Dimpy's post, the stars are congratulating him on social media. In the same post, Dimpy also shared the first picture of her son. For your information, let us tell you that Dimpy shared a picture of the child on Instagram. The baby's feet are seen in the picture. Dimpy was seen in 'Bigg Boss' season eight.

At the same time, former contestant Diandra, who took part in the show with her, commented on Dimpy's post - 'Congratulations Meri Jaan'. At the same Bindu Dara Singh could not stop herself. Along with this he also commented - 'He is born on a good day. Congratulations to you and your family. ' Dimpy married Rohit Roy in 2015 after divorcing Rahul Mahajan. Dimpy also has a daughter. Dimpy Ganguly is currently in France. She is leading a happy life with her husband and child. Along with this, Dimpy has worked in models as well as TV serials.

For your information, let us tell you that Dimpy started her career in the year 2010 with the serial 'Tujh Sang Preet Laya Sajna'. After this, worked in the serial 'Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai', 'Kahani Chandrakanta Ki', 'Sasural Genda Phool' and 'Ek Thousand Mein Meri Bahna Hai'. Along with this, apart from reality show 'Bigg Boss 8', 'Nach Baliye 5' was also seen. Along with this, Dimpy was in the limelight due to her divorce from Rahul Mahajan and some pictures from her career. In these pictures, Dimpy's face was marked with assault. At the same time, the mobile phone was said to be the reason behind Rahul's assault.
